race.comment: A few key scratchings looks to have left the door open for NOBLE CONQUEROR (4), who has placed four of seven over this mile journey and seems to be working up to another victory. Went close in a tougher race last start after being held up at a crucial stage. Can land the knockout blow this time. GREAT ASPIRATIONS (5) has been right there at the past four outings and should get a soft run in transit from gate two. Top-three conveyance. AMERICAN PHIREBALL (8) has a handy record over this course and distance with a win and four placings from seven attempts. Include in calculations. ROCK HARD LOVE (7) strips fitter third-up from the spell and may earn a cheque.
